ef=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.3171.39</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">44</biblScope> </bibl> (Orchom. <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Boeot.\">Boeot.</a></gram> </gramGrp>): generally, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">animals for slaughter,</tr_> whether for sacrifices, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:56\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.56</biblScope> </bibl>; or for food, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:207\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.207</biblScope> </bibl>; cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0028.tlg005.perseus-grc1:29\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Antipho\">Antipho</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.29</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n86798.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> prov. of stupid, lazy people, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀριθμός, πρόβατ᾽ ἄλλως</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg003.perseus-grc1:1203\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Nu.\">Nu.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1203</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:32\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">32</biblScope> </bibl>: Com. <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"comp\" opt=\"n\" TEIf