\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Opp.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ H.\">H.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.146</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0023.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:139\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.139</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0545.tlg001:9:38\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ael.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ NA\">NA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.38</biblScope></bibl>. (Orig. of small cattle, sheep and goats, which in primitive mixed herds <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">walk in front</tr_> (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">προβαίνει</etym>) of the larger animals.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}